        "subject": "LU-2622 obdclass: Use per CPU cl_env cache lists",
        "message": "LU-2622 obdclass: Use per CPU cl_env cache lists\n\nInstead of serializing access to the cl_env cache structure using a\nsingle global lock, this patch attempts to create per CPU caches for the\ncl_env structures. This allows a thread to obtain a cl_env from it's CPU\ncache with virtually no locking overhead (i.e. spin_lock/spin_unlock on\neach per CPU lock will never wait).\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: Id49ba6b24bf757c146ac913755e7509ebb8d1ecc\n"
      },
